<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>EMTHC 页面（附资助备注）</title>
  <style>
    html, body { height: 100%; margin: 0; }
    .wrap { position: fixed; inset: 0; }
    iframe {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      width: 100%; height: 100%; border: 0;
    }
    .badge {
      position: fixed; top: 12px; right: 12px; z-index: 9999;
      background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(89,193,255,.15), rgba(132,255,163,.12));
      border: 1px solid rgba(29,42,58,.6);
      border-radius: 12px; padding: 10px 14px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
      font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5; color: #9fb0c0;
      max-width: 320px;
    }
    .badge b { color: #e6edf3; }
    /* 可选：在移动端收起为一行图标，点击展开 */
    @media (max-width: 480px){
      .badge { font-size: 11px; max-width: 260px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <iframe src="https://emthc.scmzbl.com/" allow="fullscreen"></iframe>
    <div class="badge">
      四川音乐学院大学生创新创业训练计划项目：<br/>
      智“汇”民族——面向青少年的线上民族共同体意识教育平台<br/>
      <b>2025国家级项目</b>，项目编号 <b>202510654009</b> 联合研发
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
